item.title: Runescaping Series
item.dc:creator: @Andrew_Ferguson The317Guy
item.description:
@Andrew_Ferguson wrote:

Should get a notebook and spend some time writing down possible dialog for videos. Funny or odd stories about your life, cool things happening in the game/in news, stuff like that. People can go anywhere and see someone play RuneScape, give them something original they can’t find somewhere else.

item.title: Runescaping Series
item.dc:creator: @Elrick Elrick
item.description:
@Elrick wrote:

Get a headset from Turtle Beach. They’re 40 USD for a decent pair and work across platforms (at least for PC and Xbox). It helps clear out the unnecessary clanking and such that all of your videos have. Clarity increased between videos 1 and 2, but could be improved. Can still tell you’re getting comfortable with talking and recording, but overall sounds like a decent series. I personally am not interested in new RS so the content is something I cannot comment on.

item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

Good enough for a start, but you should really consider doing less live commentaries. Things like mouse clicks, keyboard sounds, or even other things that can distract you can completely throw the video off.
